 from canonical run/journal, not artifact scans.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:16:The roadmap and architecture notes both point to the same next gap: `Project & Run Record`. I’m pulling the scenario notes around project creation and durable-history-vs-runtime-log separation so the spec includes the right invariants for failure handling and query behavior.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:27:- [ ] Successful project creation writes `.ralph-burning/projects/<project-id>/project.toml`, `prompt.md`, `run.json`, `journal.ndjson`, `sessions.json`, `history/payloads/`, `history/artifacts/`, `runtime/logs/`, `runtime/backend/`, `runtime/temp/`, `amendments/`, and `rollback/`.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:29:- [ ] `run.json` persists canonical run state only: active run pointer, run status, optional stage cursor, cycle history, completion rounds, rollback-point metadata, amendment-queue state, and status summary. It must not infer state from artifacts or logs.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:31:- [ ] `sessions.json` initializes as a valid empty session store, separate from durable history.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:38:- [ ] Add payload/artifact store models and enumeration APIs for durable history. If a payload write succeeds but its artifact companion write/index fails, `run history` and `run tail` must not expose a partial durable-history record.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:39:- [ ] Runtime logs are stored and queried separately from durable history. Runtime-log write failures must not fabricate, remove, or reorder durable history.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:41:- [ ] `ralph-burning run history` shows durable history only: journal events plus payload/artifact records in canonical order. Runtime logs never appear there.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:42:- [ ] `ralph-burning run tail` shows durable history only by default, and `ralph-burning run tail --logs` appends the newest runtime logs after the durable section without changing the durable-history portion.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:45:- [ ] Add domain/unit tests for immutable flow, journal sequencing, and history/log separation; service tests with fake ports; adapter contract tests for filesystem round trips and corruption visibility; and CLI integration tests for project CRUD plus run queries.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:46:- [ ] Add public Gherkin coverage for project creation, duplicate IDs, immutable flow, list/show/delete behavior, no-active-run status, durable-history-only queries, and `run tail --logs` separation semantics.\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:53:- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/project_run_record/queries.rs` - build canonical read models for status, history, and tail\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:57:- `ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/run.rs` - implement `status`, `history`, and `tail`; keep `start`, `resume`, and `rollback` as later-slice work\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:60:- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/conformance/features/run_queries.feature` - public scenarios for status/history/tail and runtime-log separation\n/root/new-ralph-burning/.ralph/projects/ralph-burning-rewrite/loops/004-project-and-run-record-foundation/20260311194558-spec.md:63:- `ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/query_test.rs` - durable-history and runtime-log separation tests\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
